import org.apache.spark.sql.functions
wordVec: org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame = [word: string, vector: vector]

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.PCA

val pcaModel = new PCA()
    .setInputCol("vector")
    .setOutputCol("pca_vector")
    .setK(2)
    .fit(wordVec)

val pcaWordVec = pcaModel.transform(wordVec)

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._
import org.apache.spark.ml.linalg.Vector

val vec2arr = udf { v: Vector => v.toArray }

val wordPoint = pcaWordVec
    .withColumn("pca_array", vec2arr($"pca_vector"))
    .selectExpr("word", "pca_array[0] AS x", "pca_array[1] AS y")

wordPoint.write.parquet("nsmc/data/word_points.parquet")

paragraphs.text:
val findSyn = udf { word: String => model.findSynonymsArray(word, 10) }

val syn = wordVec
    .select("word")
    .withColumn("syn_sims", findSyn($"word"))
    .withColumn("syn_sim", explode($"syn_sims"))
    .selectExpr("word", "syn_sim._1 AS syn", "syn_sim._2 AS similarity")
    .union(wordVec.selectExpr("word", "word AS syn", "1.0"))

syn.write.mode("overwrite").parquet("nsmc/data/synonyms.parquet")

WITH target_syn (

    FROM syn
    WHERE word = '${단어}'

FROM target_syn sy
    JOIN word_point wp ON (sy.syn = wp.word)
